---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero2 from '../components/Hero2.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Pump Factory">
	<main>
		<Hero2 />
		<section class="about-us">
			<h1>Who we are</h1>
			<p>Welcome to Pump Factory, the ultimate destination for bouldering and climbing enthusiasts in Iloilo. Whether you are a beginner or a pro, you will find something to challenge and inspire you at our facility.</p>

				<p>
					Pump Factory is more than just a gym. It is a community of climbers who share a passion for pushing their limits, learning new skills, and having fun. Our friendly and experienced staff are always ready to help you with tips, advice, and encouragement.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					At Pump Factory, we offer a variety of climbing options to suit your preferences and goals. You can choose from over 200 bouldering problems, ranging from easy to hard, that are regularly updated by our creative route setters. You can also try our sport climbing routes, which feature top-rope and lead climbing on walls up to 15 meters high. And if you want to spice up your training, you can test your strength and endurance on our moon board, a dynamic and interactive system that allows you to climb on preset or custom-made problems.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					But Pump Factory is not only about climbing. It is also about having fun and making friends. You can relax and socialize in our spacious lounge area, where you can enjoy free Wi-Fi, snacks, and drinks. You can also join our events and workshops, where you can learn new techniques, meet new people, and have a blast.
				</p>
				
				So what are you waiting for? Come and join us at Pump Factory, where climbing is fun and fun is climbing. We look forward to seeing you soon!</p>
			<h1>Our mission</h1>

			<p>To provide a fun, safe, and supportive environment for climbers of all levels and backgrounds. We believe that climbing is more than just a sport. It is a way of life, a form of expression, and a source of joy.</p>
				
				<p>
					We are passionate about building a community of climbers who share our values of respect, integrity, and excellence. We foster a culture of friendship, collaboration, and diversity among our members and staff. We also organize events and activities to bring people together, celebrate achievements, and have fun.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					We are proud to be part of the global climbing movement, and we strive to contribute to its growth and development. We support local and international initiatives that promote climbing as a sport, a hobby, and a lifestyle. We also advocate for environmental and social responsibility, and we aim to make a positive impact on the world.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Pump Factory is more than just a gym. It is your second home, where you can find your passion, your challenge, and your tribe. Join us today and discover the amazing benefits of climbing!
				</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
    @use '../styles/style.scss';
    @use '../styles/variables' as *;
    @use '../styles/mixins' as *;

	.about-us {
		text-align: left;
		h1{
			font-size: 2rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			line-height: 1;
			margin: 1em auto;
		}
		p{
			line-height: 1.6;
			margin-bottom: 40px;
		}

	}
	.text-gradient {
		@include  text-gradient($direction, $colors);
	}


	@media (max-width: 540px) {
        h1 {
		font-size: 2rem;

	}

		.container .section-headline {
			font-size: 2rem;
			line-height: 2.5rem;
		}

    }
</style>
